data.description: Welcome to this beautiful newer home, completed in 2021, nestled in the charming Heritage Grove neighborhood within the Bridges community of Fillmore. This immaculate residence combines modern design with the warmth of a friendly community, making it the perfect place to call home.  As you approach, a spacious front porch beckons, offering a serene spot to unwind and soak in the tranquil surroundings. Step inside to discover a well-thought-out layout, boasting 3,177 square feet of living space with 4 bedrooms and 4.5 bathrooms. The convenience of a downstairs bedroom with a full bath makes it perfect for guests or multi-generational living. The heart of the home is the open floor plan, connecting the living room, dining area, and kitchen seamlessly. The kitchen features an expansive island, walk-in pantry, upgraded stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, stylish full backsplash and upgraded cabinets adorned with satin nickel hardware. Upstairs, a versatile loft space caters to your unique needs. The primary bedroom suite is a true retreat, with a separate sitting area and an ensuite bathroom with dual sinks, a separate tub, a tile-surround shower and a spacious walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms, each with walk-in closets, are located down the hall. One has an attached full bath, and the other has an adjacent full bath with dual sinks. The laundry room is conveniently situated upstairs with a sink and upper cabinets for extra storage. This home boasts tasteful upgrades like plantation shutters, roman shades, stylish fixtures, upgraded paint, ceiling fans, wood-look vinyl flooring, plush carpeting with upgraded padding, and tile flooring. The backyard is enclosed by white vinyl fencing and features a covered patio, high-quality artificial turf, decomposed granite hardscape, and lush landscaping with a lemon tree. Parking is a breeze with a 3-car tandem attached garage offering direct access to the home and an expanded driveway. Not only does this home offer style and comfort, but it is also environmentally conscious with energy-saving features including solar panels and a tankless water heater. Your peace of mind is further ensured with a security system in place. Beyond the confines of your new home, you'll find yourself within easy reach of schools, walking trails, parks, and shopping centers. The allure of nearby beach destinations and the attractions of Santa Clarita are just a short trip away. Plus, there's no HOA!
